data.description: *Huge Price Reduction* Wonderful quiet corner lot in the coveted St. Vrain Ranch Community! Pride of ownership throughout this fantastic and very spacious 4 bedroom + Loft, 3-bathroom, 3-car tandem garage w/ open floor plan and lots of natural light. A formal dining room, living room or flex space greets you upon entering.  The family room is very cozy with a gas fireplace and is situated near the large kitchen that boosts abundant Cherrywood cabinets, island and pantry. Fully unfinished basement.  The private master has vaulted ceilings, 5-piece bath and large walk-in closet.  The laundry area is conveniently located on the upper floor!  A nice sized backyard with vinyl fencing and a large patio for those summer evenings that will not disappoint.  This home is two blocks from Patterson Park, The Dog Park and only a five-minute walk to the elementary and middle school.  Enjoy being close to town, amenities, shops & restaurants w/ quick access to I-25!
